{"tid":221594,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人記得當年皇室堡單野","createTime":"2017-04-28T21:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T19:05:29.000Z","uid":1020,"like":9,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"869bf528af66662b2a422dcec8612ebdba3a2b80","tid":221594,"uid":1020,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T21:05:04.000Z","msg":"個小朋友細細個就冇老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18153aa89d06c3d195ef2e6da8b5a5714deb516b","tid":221594,"uid":69877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T21:20:55.000Z","msg":"唉 買左爆谷都食唔到"},{"pid":"77559dd7511a2fc87fa403056dae70b90f7dff0b","tid":221594,"uid":37566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T21:23:04.000Z","msg":"睇返當年啲新聞每次都好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3321043130e03f9a16a729627aa9c16025ab2db","tid":221594,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T21:24:19.000Z","msg":"狐仙簡單來說就是一種由狐狸修練成的妖精，有善有惡。二十多年前，香港便傳出幾起關於狐仙的都市傳說，據傳，在銅鑼灣現已改名為「皇室堡」的溫莎公爵大廈，其三樓有一間酒樓，某天晚上，有一對夫婦包下酒樓全場，請賓客喝兒子的滿月酒。當晚夫婦睡著後，太太做了一個噩夢。 <br />\n<br />\n夢中她見到一隻紅眼尖牙的狐狸向她怒罵：「你們在我的地方請滿月酒，竟然不給我面子來敬我一杯，我要吃掉你的嬰孩！」話說完便把嬰孩咬死。太太驚醒後，立即叫醒丈夫並告訴他剛才做的夢，二人立即去看寶寶，沒想到寶寶居然面如死灰也停止呼吸，送醫後仍告不治，醫院證實嬰兒為突發性死亡。 <br />\n後來這對夫婦去酒樓查看，見到酒樓的大理石外牆，浮現一顆狐狸的頭。新聞媒報導之後，事件愈鬧愈大，狐仙咬死嬰孩傳遍全香港，許多民眾紛紛到酒樓來看傳聞中的狐仙。 <br />\n大廈業主為免引起社會恐慌，便要保全用布將大理石牆遮住，後來才將大理石牆拆除，事件從此便不了了之。另一說法是，該事件發生地，是在溫莎公爵大廈對面的某酒樓。另一次狐仙事件，據傳也有一名嬰孩受害！"},{"pid":"2ea76e53d938514798c781f49f6e1765b06ffe0a","tid":221594,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T21:24:38.000Z","msg":"德仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d509e44c9a4defa07b8079bf3b76df3e6f3682a9","tid":221594,"uid":588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T21:58:03.000Z","msg":"係咪講緊90年代湖南幫嗰單嘢？"},{"pid":"2c8a7e0d2e1bff6b0c56a176ebee839e9a257b07","tid":221594,"uid":53765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T21:58:47.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1870ce27344228600a61d23f19a182248b4ebac5","tid":221594,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:09:17.000Z","msg":"德仔老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6816c4daac098aaa4740b3a3e261f01ad0daca4","tid":221594,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:18:06.000Z","msg":"湖南仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a1f5d3d1e26cfab83342d0973c9825ad983bb9","tid":221594,"uid":115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:20:11.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打一齊做帛金<br />\n暑名用有心人 定 無名氏好"},{"pid":"80ec3fd03c1f2b4a9ac3f245895c59dc1c8dad5b","tid":221594,"uid":28201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>湖南仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啱想講，湖南仔都死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e902f950e8226b123813de6d9acb63be5ed7cb1","tid":221594,"uid":69877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:29:29.000Z","msg":"聽講個朝班賊仲去左皇室堡樓上飲完茶先做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7891aaee2148acd53c41a3bf385c277c5f8293d","tid":221594,"uid":30952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:40:18.000Z","msg":"好撚悶啊<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"73b003e0a06269c3a4e1c0e1e21ded0865eb513f","tid":221594,"uid":1020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T23:51:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b12bab37eb84d9c39479eda59736f3d4895a285","tid":221594,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:58:29.000Z","msg":"依加仲未拉到個刀手"},{"pid":"c78453b3b15c922f7a65ea06fe9e7b3c70290190","tid":221594,"uid":2636,"like":0,"dislik